  <description>
    <p>WebP Converter allows you to convert images to the WebP format. It is on average 93% faster than online alternatives, with no limit on amount of converts and ability to control compression quality.</p>
    <p>With a compression setting of 60, you will notice minimal reduction in quality while shrinking file size to around 90% of its original size.</p>
  </description>
